ds/2024/07/Jonny-Greenwood-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonny-Greenwood-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonny-Greenwood-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonny-Greenwood-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonny-Greenwood-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonny-Greenwood-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>随着<a href="/artists/Jonny-Greenwood">乔尼·格林伍德</a>从重症监护室康复中恢复过来，<a href="/artists/The-Smile">微笑乐队</a>取消了即将到来的八月份欧洲巡演日期。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-smile-london-hammersmith-apollo-radiohead-review-setlist-photos-3599692">The Smile 伦敦现场演出：Radiohead 在全新世界中的爵士朋克冒险</a></strong></li></ul><p>该乐队由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/radiohead">Radiohead</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thom-yorke">Thom Yorke</a>和 Jonny Greenwood 以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sons-of-kemet">Sons Of Kemet</a>鼓手 Tom Skinner 组成，他们在 Instagram 官方账户上更新了 Greenwood 的健康状况以及取消巡演的原因。</p><p> “几天前，乔尼因感染而病重，需要紧急住院治疗，其中一些在重症监护室治疗。幸运的是，他现在已脱离危险，很快就会回家。”他们在声明中说道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9U670wu8iX/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" backgro